mischen L\u00e4nder |date=1996 |issue=37 |pages=98\u2013119 |url=https://biblio.hiu.cas.cz/documents/19854 |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite journal |last1=Hradsk\u00e1 |first1=Katar\u00edna |translator-last=Hennerov\u00e1|translator-first=Magdalena|title=Vorgeschichte der slowakischen Transporte nach Theresienstadt|trans-title=The History of Slovak Transports to Theresienstadt |journal=Theresienst\u00e4dter Studien und Dokumente |date=1996 |issue=3 |pages=82\u201397 |id={{CEEOL|274407}} |ref=harv |language=German}}\n*{{cite journal |last1=Johnson |first1=Owen V. |title=\u017didovsk\u00e1 komunita na Slovensku medzi ceskoslovenskou parlamentnou demokraciou a slovensk\u00fdm \u0161t\u00e1tom v stredoeur\u00f3pskom kontexte, Eduard Ni\u017enansk\u00fd (Pre\u0161ov, Slovakia: Universum, 1999), 292 pp., 200 crowns (Slovak). |journal=Holocaust and Genocide Studies |date=2005 |volume=19 |issue=2 |pages=314\u2013317 |doi=10.1093/hgs/dci033|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite journal |last1=Kamenec |first1=Ivan |title=Fenom\u00e9n korupcie v procese tzv. rie\u0161enia \"\u017eidovskej ot\u00e1zky\" na Slovensku v rokoch 1938\u20131945 |trans-title=The phenomenon of corruption in the so-called solutions to the \"Jewish questions\" in Slovakia between 1938 and 1945 |pp=96\u2013112 |journal=Forum Historiae |date=2011 |volume=5 |issue=2 |url=http://forumhistoriae.sk/-/fenomen-korupcie-v-procese-tzv-riesenia-zidovskej-otazky-na-slovensku-v-rokoch-1938-1945 |ref={{sfnref|Kamenec|2011b}} |language=sk |issn=1337-6861 |access-date=17 December 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006075629/http://forumhistoriae.sk/-/fenomen-korupcie-v-procese-tzv-riesenia-zidovskej-otazky-na-slovensku-v-rokoch-1938-1945 |archive-date=6 October 2018 |url-status=dead }}\n*{{cite journal |last1=Ni\u017e\u0148ansk\u00fd |first1=Eduard |title=On Relations between the Slovak Majority and Jewish Minority During World War II |journal=[[Yad Vashem Studies]] |date=2014 |volume=42 |issue=2 |pages=47-90 |issn=0084-3296|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite journal |first=Nina |last1=Paulovi\u010dov\u00e1 |title=Holocaust Memory and Antisemitism in Slovakia: The Postwar Era to the Present |journal=[[Antisemitism Studies]]|publisher=Indiana University Press |date=2018 |volume=2 |issue=1 |pages=4\u201334|doi=10.2979/antistud.2.1.02|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite journal |last1=Ward |first1=James Mace |title=\"People Who Deserve It\": Jozef Tiso and the Presidential Exemption |journal=Nationalities Papers |date=2002 |volume=30 |issue=4 |pages=571\u2013601 |doi=10.1080/00905992.2002.10540508|ref=harv|issn=1465-3923}}\n{{refend}}\n\n====Theses====\n{{refbegin|35em|indent=yes}}\n*{{cite thesis|degree=PhD |last1=Paulovi\u010dov\u00e1 |first1=Nina |title=Rescue of Jews in the Slovak State (1939\u20131945) |date=2012 |url=https://era.library.ualberta.ca/items/e8340da1-7b46-40cc-95e1-d57665a23e34 |language=en|doi=10.7939/R33H33|institution=[[University of Alberta]]|ref=harv|location=Edmonton}}\n*{{cite thesis|last=Put\u00edk|first=Daniel|title=Sloven\u0161t\u00ed \u017did\u00e9 v Terez\u00edn\u011b, Sachsenhausenu, Ravensbr\u00fccku a Bergen-Belsenu, 1944/1945|language=cs|trans-title=Slovak Jews in Theresienstadt, Sachsenhausen, Ravensbr\u00fcck and Bergen-Belsen, 1944/1945|date=2015|degree=PhD|url=https://is.cuni.cz/webapps/zzp/detail/104422/?lang=en|institution=[[Charles University]]|location=Prague|ref=harv|postscript=. English-language abstract pp. 203\u2013216.}}\n{{refend}}\n\n====''Encyclopedia of Camps and Ghettos''====\n{{main|Encyclopedia of Camps and Ghettos, 1933\u20131945}}\n\n=====Volume 2\u2014[https://www.ushmm.org/research/publications/encyclopedia-camps-ghettos open access]=====\n{{refbegin|35em|indent=yes}}\n*{{cite encyclopedia |last=Crago|first=Laura|entry=Lublin Region (Distrikt Lublin)|pp=604\u2013609|title=Ghettos in German-Occupied Eastern Europe|series=Encyclopedia of Camps and Ghettos, 1933\u20131945 |volume=2|editor1-last=Geoffrey P.|editor1-first=Megargee|editor1-link=Geoffrey P. Megargee|editor2-l